The paper proposes a novel approach to few-shot learning using machine learning tools such as ridge regression and logistic regression. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves deep learning and back-propagation, which are common in the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which are common in the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
